<h4>1. Add snowagent to application Gemfile</h4>
<code>
gem 'snowagent'
</code>

<h4>2. Configure application</h4>
<b>Heroku:</b>
<pre>
heroku config:set \
  SNOWMANIO_SERVER={{base_url}} \
  SNOWMANIO_SECRET_TOKEN={{token}}
</pre>

<b>Standalone:</b><br>
<pre>
# Add environment variables to production application
SNOWMANIO_SERVER={{info.base_url}}
SNOWMANIO_SECRET_TOKEN={{app.token}}
</pre>

<h2>Send Test Request</h2>
<pre>
curl {{base_url}}/agent/metrics -d '{"token":"{{token}}","metrics":[{"name":"request","value":0.15,"kind":"request"}]}'
</pre>
